00:00:44.133 --> 00:00:45.773
which is right over here.

00:00:45.773 --> 00:00:48.470
So, that's the point X equals C,

00:00:48.470 --> 00:00:50.434
and then, this value, of course,

00:00:50.434 --> 00:00:53.337
is going to be F of C.

00:00:53.337 --> 00:00:54.709
F of C.

