00:01:40.972 --> 00:01:43.613
And so, we could take the limit...

00:01:44.811 --> 00:01:48.134
The limit as X approaches C,

00:01:48.134 --> 00:01:50.846
as X approaches C,

00:01:50.846 --> 00:01:54.301
of the slope of this secant line.

